comments: VanVleet (HOU) briefly places his hands against Gobert (MIN) and immediately removes them as Gobert rolls to the basket.
Smith Jr. (HOU) places a resting hand against Conley's (MIN) side contesting his driving shot attempt.
Conley (MIN) places his hand on Green's (HOU) shoulder but the contact is marginal as Green briefly loses control of his dribble.
Conley (MIN) is established in a legally obtained position when VanVleet (HOU) steps forwards and incidental foot contact occurs.
Gobert (MIN) brings a hand to VanVleet's (HOU) front, but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Edwards (MIN) extends his hands into Smith Jr. (HOU), affecting his ability to receive the throw-in.
Anderson (MIN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Smith Jr. (HOU) briefly places a hand on Edwards' (MIN) body as he contests, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his dunk.

Green (HOU) grazes Edwards' (MIN) head during his dunk.   Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
McDaniels (MIN) leaves a foot planted in Green's (HOU) path and he initiates foot-to-foot contact that causes Green to trip.

VanVleet (HOU) wraps his arms around Edwards' (MIN) body and initiates illegal contact during his drive in transition. After communicating with the Replay Center, it is confirmed that the foul meets the criteria for a clear-path foul.
Green (HOU) engages with Alexander-Walker (MIN) during the throw-in but does not affect his FOM.
Alexander-Walker (MIN) is already losing control of his dribble when Green (HOU) reaches in and marginal contact occurs.
McDaniels (MIN) loses his footing on his own, and not as a result of any illegal contact.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Alexander-Walker (MIN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
VanVleet (HOU) commits a take foul on Conley (MIN).
Edwards (MIN) places his forearm against VanVleet's (HOU) side and marginal contact occurs during VanVleet's drive.
Green (HOU) grabs the ball after the made basket.
Green (HOU) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN).
Green (HOU) gathers the ball at the end of his drive and Edwards (MIN) initiates contact with Green's arm affecting his SQBR.
Conley (MIN) brushes VanVleet's (HOU) arm as he gathers the inbounds pass.
